\c 8
\s Vana vaBhenjamini naSauro
\p
\v 1 Bhenjamini akabereka mwana wake wedangwe Bhera, naAshibheri wechipiri, naAhara wechitatu;
\v 2 naNowa wechina, naRafa weshanu.
\v 3 Bhera akabereka vanakomana: Adhari, naGera naAbhihudhi;
\v 4 naAbhishua, naNaamani, naAhoa;
\v 5 naGera, naShefufani, naHurami.
\v 6 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaEhudhi: Ndivo vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba aigara paGebha, vakavatapa, vakaenda navo Manahati;
\v 7 naNaamani, naAhiya, naGera, iye akavatapa; akabereka Uza naAhihudhi.
\v 8 Shaharaimi akabereka vanakomana panyika yaMoabhi, adzinga vakadzi vake Hushimi naBhaara.
\v 9 Akabereka kumukadzi wake Hodheshi: Jobhabhu, naZibhia, naMesha, naMarikami;
\v 10 naJeuzi, naShakia, naMirima. Ndivo vanakomana vake, vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba.
\v 11 Hushimi akabereka Abhitubhi naEripaari.
\v 12 Vanakomana vaEripaari: Ebheri, naMishami, naShemedhi; ndiye wakavaka Ono, naRodhi, nemisha yawo;
\v 13 naBheira, naShema, ivo vaiva vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba aigara paAjaroni, vakadzinga vakange vagere paGati;
\v 14 naAhiyo, naShashaki, naJeremoti;
\v 15 naZebhedhia, naAradhi, naEdheri;
\v 16 naMikaeri, naIshipa, naJoha, ivo vanakomana vaBheira;
\v 17 naZebhedhia, naMeshurami, naHiziki, naHebheri;
\v 18 naIshimerai, naIziria, naJobhabhu, ivo vanakomana vaEripaari;
\v 19 naJakimi, naZikiri, naZabhudhi;
\v 20 naErienai, naZiretai, naErieri;
\v 21 naAdhaya, naBheraya, naShimirati, ivo vanakomana VaShimei;
\v 22 naIshipani, naEbheri, naErieri;
\v 23 naAbhidhoni, naZikiri, naHanani;
\v 24 naHanania, naErami, naAnatotiya;
\v 25 naIfudheya, naPenueri, ivo vanakomana vaShashaki;
\v 26 naShamisherai, neSheharia, naAtaria;
\v 27 naJareshia, naEria, naZikiri, ivo vanakomana vaJehorami.
\v 28 Ivo vaiva vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba kumarudzi avo ese, vakuru; ivo vaigara Jerusarema.
\p
\v 29 PaGibhiyoni paigara baba vaGibhiyoni, wainzi Jeyieri, zita romukadzi wake rakange riri Maaka.
\p
\v 30 Mwanakomana wake wedangwe aiva Abhidhoni, naZuri, naKishi, naBhaari, naNadhabhi;
\v 31 naGedhori, naAhio, naZekariya.
\v 32 Mikiroti akabereka Shimea. Naivo vaigara nehama dzavo Jerusarema, vakatarisana nehama dzavo.
\p
\v 33 Neri akabereka Kishi, Kishi akabereka Sauro, Sauro akabereka Jonatani, naMariki-Shua, naAbhinadhabhu, naEshibhaari.
\v 34 Mwanakomana waJonatani akange ari Meribhibhaari; Meribhibhaari akabereka Mika.
\v 35 Vanakomana vaMika: Pitoni, naMereki, naTarea, naAhazi.
\v 36 Ahazi akabereka Joadha, Joadha akabereka Arimeti, naAzimavheti, naZimiri; Zimiri akabereka Moza;
\v 37 Moza akabereka Bhinea; Rafa waiva mwanakomana wake, naEreasa mwanakomana wake, naAzeri mwanakomana wake.
\v 38 Azeri wakange ana vanakomana vatanhatu; mazita avo ndiwo: Azirikami, naBhokeru, naIshimaeri, naShearia, naObhadhiya, naHanani. Ava vese vaiva vanakomana vaAzeri.
\v 39 Vanakomana vaEsheki munin'ina wake: Urami mwanakomana wake wedangwe, naJeuzi wechipiri, naErifereti wechitatu.
\v 40 Vanakomana vaUrami vaiva varume vane simba noumhare, vapfuri vemiseve; vakange vana vanakomana vazhinji, navanakomana vavanakomana vavo, vakasvika zana namakumi mashanu. Ivo vese vaiva vanakomana vaBhenjamini.